OL,5, Business leaders have urged the prime  
OL,6, minister to make this year's extra bank
OL,7, holiday marking the Queen's Platinum   
OL,8, Jubilee permanent.                     
OL,10,FIn an open letter, the CBI, UK         
OL,11,FHospitality and a host of well-known   
OL,12,Fbrands said a "thank holiday" would    
OL,13,Fhonour the monarch and public service. 
OL,15,FThey argued that the new holiday would 
OL,16,Fprovide an economic boost after Covid. 
OL,18,FResearch by PwC also suggests that     
OL,19,Fgovernment figures have overestimated  
OL,20,Fthe cost of a new bank holiday by 64%. 
